   CME0558

   Blessed with a body like an hourglass? Good for you girl. PLT Shape is
   designed with you in mind, with a few figure and curve enhancing tweaks
   to give you the perfect fit.

   Shape Black Collar Detail Hook And Eye Bodycon Dress

   Refresh your little black dress collection with this killer style.
   Featuring a black material with hook and eye detailing, a plunging
   neckline and a figure-hugging fit. Style this with barely-there heels
   and a hair clip to complete the look.

     Length approx 84cm/33" (Based on a sample size UK 8)

     Model wears size UK 8/ EU 36/ AUS 8/ US 4

     Model Height - 5ft 5”
   Fabric & Care

   95% Polyester 5% Elastane

   Please note: due to fabric used, colour may transfer.
