   Red Polka Dot Tie Front Frill Hem Bodycon Dress

   This polka dot dress is perfect for any off-duty antics. Featuring a
   red polka dot material with a tie front detail and a frill hem, team it
   with some strappy sandals and a mini bag for a chic day-to-night combo.

     Length approx 91cm/36" (Based on a sample size UK 8)

     Model wears size UK 8/ EU 36/ AUS 8/ US 4

     Model Height - 5ft 9”
   Fabric & Care

   95% Viscose 5% Elastane

   Please note: due to fabric used, colour may transfer.
