   White Strappy Binding Bodice Detail Midi Dress

   Switch up your weekend look with this dreamy dress. Featuring a white
   material, bodice detailing and a flattering midi fit, what's not to
   love? Style this dress with clear heels and simple accessories for day
   drinks with the dolls.

     Length approx 109cm/43" (Based on a sample size UK 8)

     Model wears size UK 8/ EU 36/ AUS 8/ US 4

     Model Height - 5ft 8”
