   Petrol Blue Bardot Puff Sleeve Midi Dress

   Get ready for that special date in your diary with this midi dress.
   Featuring a petrol blue material with a bardot neckline and puff
   sleeves, team it with some strappy heels and a mini bag for a look
   we're loving.

     Length approx 101.5cm/40" (Based on a sample size UK 8)

     Model wears size UK 8/ EU 36/ AUS 8/ US 4

     Model Height - 5ft 7”
   Fabric & Care

   95% Polyester 5% Elastane

   Please note: due to fabric used, colour may transfer.
